OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrance moves closer to ban 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon hair discrimination     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, France has moved a step closer to      
OL,6, banning discrimination in the workplace
OL,7, against hairstyles.                    
OL,9,FA bill has been approved in the        
OL,10,FNational Assembly and will now be      
OL,11,Fdebated in the Senate.                 
OL,13,FThe law will bar employers from        
OL,14,Frequiring hair to be straightened and  
OL,15,Ffor afros, dreadlocks and braids to be 
OL,16,Fcovered.                               
OL,18,FIts author hopes the law will support  
OL,19,Fthose, particularly black people, who  
OL,20,Fhave faced workplace hostility.        
